{
  "title": "Rich Earthy Ethiopian Mackerel Azifa",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful Ethiopian dish featuring mackerel, tempering chocolate, and earthy spices, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This vegetarian-friendly azifa is a unique and exciting meal prep option.",
  "cuisine": "Ethiopian",
  "diet": [
